## Example environment variables (DO NOT put real secrets here)

## OpenAlex configuration
OPENALEX_API_TOKEN="<openalex_api_token>"
OPENALEX_USER_AGENT="mailto:contact@example.org"

## REDCap configuration
REDCAP_API_URL="https://redcap.example.com/api"
REDCAP_API_TOKEN="<redcap_api_token>"

## npm registry auth (used by CI release workflow; mirrors `secrets.NPM_TOKEN`)
NPM_TOKEN="<npm_token>"
